    General Stores in Santacruz, Mumbai

    (1296 Ratings & Reviews) 4.0 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Santacruz, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. In marketing terminology, a kirana shop is a form of traditional retail catering to the needs of citizens. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. Please scroll up to find a list of General Stores in Santacruz, Mumbai.
